  - Discernment-Truth=The Eye Of Eternity-Supreme Center=The Eternal Now
By: Parmenides
---
Being is without beginning and indestructible; it is universal, existing alone,
immovable and without end; nor ever was it nor will it be, since it now is, all
together, one, and continuous.
